<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
	<title>about</title>
	<style>	
	header{
	text-align:center;
	height:40px;
	color:blue;
	background-color : pink;
}

	#about{
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: white;
    color: black;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 80px 10%;
}

.about-container{
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 60px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.about-image img{
    width: 350px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(56,189,248,0.3);
}

/* CONTENT */

.about-content{
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 300px;
}
h2{
    font-size: 45px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color:#556B2F ;
}

    p{
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    color:#1a1a1a;
}

/* INFO BOXES */

.about-boxes{
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 30px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.box{
    background: skyblue;
    padding: 20px 30px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: 0.3s;
}

.box:hover{
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    background: pink;
}

.box h3{
    font-size: 28px;
    color: #1a1a1a;
}

.box span{
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #1a1a1a;
}


</style>
	</head>
	<body>
	
		<header>
		<h1 >About Me...</h1></header>

		<p>Name : Jyotsna Muripindi</p>
		<p>Date of Birth : 15-06-2006 </p>
		
	
  <p>
    I'm Jyotsna, a Computer Science and Systems Engineering student
    passionate about creating modern and responsive web applications.
  </p>

  <p>
    I enjoy learning new technologies and improving my problem-solving
    skills through practical projects and continuous practice.
  </p>

  <p>
    Currently, I am exploring frontend and backend development while
    building projects to strengthen my technical knowledge.
  </p>
 <div class="about-boxes">

        <div class="box">
          <h3>2</h3>
          <span>Projects</span>
        </div>

        <div class="box">
          <h3>5+</h3>
          <span>Certificates</span>
        </div>

        <div class="box">
          <h3>3rd Year</h3>
          <span>Student</span>
        </div>

	</body>
</html>
